Context("LimitedNumeric");

do {
   $original = random(10,80,1);
   $inc = random(5,20,1);
} until (int($inc/$original*10000)!=$inc/$original*10000);

$new = $original+$inc;
$decIncNotRounded = $inc/$original;
$decInc = sprintf("%.4f",$decIncNotRounded);
$perInc = $decInc*100;

Context("LimitedPercent-strict");
Context()->flags->set(
   trimTrailingZeros => 1,
   decimalPlaces => 2,
   tolerance => .00005,
);
$ans = Compute("$perInc %");

##############################################

TEXT(beginproblem());

BEGIN_PGML

The population of cats in a shelter increased from [`[$original]`] to [`[$new]`]. What is the percentage increase of the shelter's cat population?

[@KeyboardInstructions('Fill in the blank with percent. Round your answer to [`2`] decimal places, like [`12.34%`].')@]**

The percentage increase is approximately [________]{$ans}.

END_PGML

